Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫葛拉丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.79,0:00:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就将我当成身为勇者的你的敌人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.34,0:00:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一击就将噬魂者给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这挂也开得太厉害了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颤抖停不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.81,0:00:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的浪潮之战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.05,0:02:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不出招吗勇者尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.01,0:02:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的仆人也出招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仆人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文的仆人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然只有这么点力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮舞零之型·逆式雪月花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只是仆人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹让我享受一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思我没打算享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.09,0:04:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这点毒性就能打倒我了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.23,0:04:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速踢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间就踢了8次很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你踢不中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩到我身边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.51,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆式雪月花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能接下我的招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.11,0:05:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你什么时候会使用刚才那面火焰一般的盾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧愤怒之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧打不中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅菲洛交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.47,0:06:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这火的温度对我来说太低了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮舞破之型·裝甲割
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个攻击还不能打倒你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.45,0:06:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的防御力倒是很符合勇者之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能得你夸奖我很荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过黑色火焰只有受到近距离攻击才会发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到远距离攻击不会发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有绝招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用藏拙让我见识一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.30,0:07:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然话说到这份上那我就满足你的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.77,0:07:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转换形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁处女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没我想的那么强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辜负我的期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么有什么办法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.68,0:07:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了吗没想到这么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.81,0:07:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发令之后你就发动光魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪潮之战就以我们的胜利告终吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我和你无冤无仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初级照明术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初级治愈术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.04,0:08:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无谓的挣扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人攻击来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵气盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么远无法将他们彻底打倒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.72,0:09:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我就撤退了以你们的力量活不过下次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.85,0:09:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在浪潮中胜利的是我们请别忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算成功逃脱了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.57,0:10:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然出现的倒计时恐怕是浪潮结束的时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说到底浪潮到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.49,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是毁灭世界的灾害吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.71,0:10:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫葛拉丝的女人很执着于打倒身为勇者的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.04,0:10:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始真正的浪潮之战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.55,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是谜团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.47,0:10:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们必须在下次浪潮到来前变得更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然下次一定会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让盾吸收魔物的碎片就能得到新技能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.61,0:10:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要从根本上进行强化还是得让拉芙塔莉雅和菲洛升阶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那个勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧来城堡进行报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.63,0:11:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转换形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.97,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁处女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过水晶球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.62,0:11:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你镇压了浪潮虽然让我感到非常遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是向人道谢的态度吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.59,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白您的心情但是请和骑士团长一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.93,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是如何得到这份力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.90,0:12:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得到了与盾之勇者不符的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要说出这个秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.49,0:12:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧不许撒谎说出真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道就跪下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.29,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所在的世界想请教的时候必须把头贴到地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.80,0:12:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说「拜托了请告诉无知的我」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.84,0:12:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我可以当场杀了你直接杀出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.39,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚张声势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.06,0:12:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想和打倒了浪潮怪物的我战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.03,0:12:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪潮结束、回到原本的世界前我会在最低限度上协助你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不许再妨碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.96,0:13:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然对国王不敬不能放过你盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.68,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了让你那些可恨的奴隶来赎罪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你用什么肮脏的手段我都会保护同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让你们从我这里夺走任何事物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你碰一下她们试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.49,0:13:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会追杀你到天涯海角让你后悔自己被生下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:14:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次的活跃非常漂亮是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.06,0:14:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为勇者大人的活跃大家不得不承认您的功绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.07,0:14:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中也有敌视您的势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.91,0:14:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善意是表面其背后是暗中活动及阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.04,0:14:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后您应该更谨慎地行动是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是也?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂有事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说您方才在和盾之勇者典人交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.27,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还听说交谈在剑拔弩张的气氛下结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.32,0:14:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲在与盾之勇者不和的情况下无法对抗浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至会影响国家的安稳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您与他和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他和解?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有生你的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.88,0:15:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲为什么如此讨厌盾之勇者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.10,0:15:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让他和亚人嚣张起来家人又会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然顶嘴太无礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.61,0:15:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今女王不在国王的意见是绝对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.61,0:15:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我们王女来说也不例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲是国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.33,0:15:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有你不能理解的行为都是为了这个国家着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.67,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也明白你姻今还是想向父亲撒娇的年龄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是节制一些吧梅尔蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我身为姐姐的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.39,0:16:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您的忠告不过这件事和姐姐没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.14,0:16:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和父亲母亲一样担忧这个国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.48,0:16:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是将要继承王位之人的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么容我告辞父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.62,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.15,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你居然真的会和国王吵起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.15,0:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(458.667,46)}注:喧を壳る,「壳る」的意思为卖,直译为卖吵架/打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没吵是对方先开口找茬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.15,0:17:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的你要买东西在我店里买就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过升阶的事情你要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.58,0:17:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下不会让你用龙刻沙漏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算去席德威鲁特或席德弗里登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你总有一天会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我推荐你去席德弗里登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶商人也推荐我去席德弗里登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说那里虽然是亚人的国家但是对人类也很宽容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.14,0:17:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯另一个席德咸鲁特是亚人绝对主义的极端国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.77,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果是盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.44,0:17:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人又要出门吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.78,0:17:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐马车大概需要1个月如果是菲洛鸟小姑娘会更快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要的东西我会斟酌着帮你装进车里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有给拉芙塔莉雅换一把剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑有预备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是长途旅行得节约一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.10,0:18:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这么快就能出发了埃尔哈特先生的效率还是那么高呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送了你点道具当做饯别礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果喜欢的话就用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给小哥的是盾上的装饰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.79,0:18:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以详细调查盾做到各种各样的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给小姑娘一把剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你准备了一把剑和之前折断那把一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用得顺手的剑比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再给你一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔力剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对没有实体的敌人很有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.35,0:18:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了预防菲洛鸟小姑娘万一不能拉马车时备的帮忙道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这玩意在就可以以一顶百
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了它小哥你也能拉马车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.55,0:19:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行真好不会被任何人束缚非常自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用和王族及其他勇者扯上关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.82,0:19:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人虽然时间短暂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.95,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔快来这边这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她是曾经和我们一起旅行的同伴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.62,0:19:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人小梅尔是好孩子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请您回到王都再次与奥托克雷王见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.61,0:20:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望您为自己对国王的失礼道歉与他和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.03,0:20:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.16,0:20:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止浪潮需要勇者大人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.74,0:20:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时勇者大人也需要国王的援助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.46,0:20:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,援助?在帮忙的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只在浪潮结束之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也是王族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.68,0:20:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这样你和父亲都这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.40,0:21:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者和国王绝对不能互相敌视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.82,0:21:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菲洛你也这么想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.11,0:21:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅也这么认为吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我我是尚文大人的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看大家都这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了好好向父亲道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然父亲会被母亲斥责的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气的样子和她爸一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲会被母亲斥责?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好听我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和当时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.32,0:21:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人想要陷害我的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说回到王都
